Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.65,1:46:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a moment....I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.36,1:46:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell address
Dialogue: 0,1:46:53.01,1:46:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, the long and severe winter has ended
Dialogue: 0,1:46:56.84,1:47:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and the beautiful Sakura flowers began to bloom
Dialogue: 0,1:47:00.93,1:47:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon-chan, Saki-chan, C-chan
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.01,1:47:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulation on your graduation
Dialogue: 0,1:47:06.66,1:47:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like just yesterday
Dialogue: 0,1:47:09.88,1:47:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura Gakuin 2015nendo started on May
Dialogue: 0,1:47:13.68,1:47:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel it like a dream
Dialogue: 0,1:47:17.14,1:47:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,that almost one year has already passed since then
Dialogue: 0,1:47:20.60,1:47:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking back on this year,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:23.06,1:47:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,we've made so many memories 
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.04,1:47:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day on May,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.98,1:47:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,when we had a photo-shooting,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:30.85,1:47:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we met the transfer-ins for the first time
Dialogue: 0,1:47:32.85,1:47:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,as many as SIX girls
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.38,1:47:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them were so energetic
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.50,1:47:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I had had only one year career as a Sakura girl,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:41.31,1:47:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but honestly, 
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.86,1:47:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I suspected that it's difficult to keep the good tradition of Sakura Gakuin
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.73,1:47:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I found three of you seniors
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.80,1:47:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,were also with an anxious look on your face
Dialogue: 0,1:47:53.72,1:47:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But before long,
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.00,1:48:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you showed us your hopeful attitude
Dialogue: 0,1:48:00.48,1:48:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,, toward making new Sakura Gakuin
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.24,1:48:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than the anxiety 
Dialogue: 0,1:48:08.18,1:48:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Three of you have been kind and generous 
Dialogue: 0,1:48:10.57,1:48:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but once in a while, you taught us strictly
Dialogue: 0,1:48:14.92,1:48:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,how to make the very best performance with 12 of us
Dialogue: 0,1:48:18.68,1:48:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,or how each member can make an improvement 
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.38,1:48:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your harsh words made us realize
Dialogue: 0,1:48:25.39,1:48:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,that we had been neglecting the effort to improve ourselves
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.54,1:48:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,or that we had been just satisfied with what we used to be
Dialogue: 0,1:48:32.80,1:48:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We were annoyed by our own simple-mindedness and sometimes shed tears
Dialogue: 0,1:48:37.08,1:48:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirai Saki-chan, the Talk Chairperson
Dialogue: 0,1:48:40.01,1:48:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She is 15, but she is said to be like an office-clerk
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.73,1:48:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,as this, she is matured in her appearance and mind
Dialogue: 0,1:48:45.73,1:48:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and she is kinda smart
Dialogue: 0,1:48:47.56,1:48:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So she is likely to be seen as a down-to-earth girl
Dialogue: 0,1:48:50.26,1:48:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But actually, she sometimes is clumsy and goofy 
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.92,1:48:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, she sometimes stumbles over nothing and falls down
Dialogue: 0,1:48:55.78,1:48:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,or, she once dropped and lost her bank-card
Dialogue: 0,1:48:58.89,1:49:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When she runs, she leans forward and looks funny
Dialogue: 0,1:49:03.54,1:49:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And, C-chan is...
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.68,1:49:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,not only a member of Sakura Gakuin
Dialogue: 0,1:49:07.85,1:49:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but also a dedicated Fukei-san
Dialogue: 0,1:49:11.70,1:49:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of her Fukei-sb...Fukei-spirit,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.23,1:49:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,she is highly observant to each one of members
Dialogue: 0,1:49:18.04,1:49:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,far higher than I expected
Dialogue: 0,1:49:22.16,1:49:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She has been looking at us so carefully
Dialogue: 0,1:49:24.90,1:49:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that she once asserted "As for the MCing, I know..."
Dialogue: 0,1:49:27.10,1:49:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"what you're good at,"
Dialogue: 0,1:49:29.10,1:49:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"and what you're bad at"
Dialogue: 0,1:49:34.04,1:49:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before a concert,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:35.88,1:49:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,she gave us good advice on
Dialogue: 0,1:49:38.85,1:49:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,what we should talk on the stage
Dialogue: 0,1:49:42.94,1:49:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Every one of us loves such caring C-chan
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.28,1:49:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,C-chan,
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.75,1:49:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you gave us wonderful advice from the perspective of  a customer
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.71,1:49:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,which is hard to know for us
Dialogue: 0,1:49:53.71,1:49:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We could realize several things thanks to your advice 
Dialogue: 0,1:49:56.64,1:49:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and that motivated us a lot to entertain Fukei-sans more
Dialogue: 0,1:49:59.98,1:50:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:50:02.67,1:50:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooga Saki-chan, the Education Chairperson
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.10,1:50:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She once poured barley tea into her glasses-case, half-asleep
Dialogue: 0,1:50:08.05,1:50:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And in our streaming program LoGiRL,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:10.97,1:50:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,she so often give strange and funny answers at quiz-segment
Dialogue: 0,1:50:13.80,1:50:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She has strong feelings for singing
Dialogue: 0,1:50:16.40,1:50:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and sometimes she sang so emotionally that the song sounded like an Enka-ballad
Dialogue: 0,1:50:21.04,1:50:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,At a break time in a lesson, 
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.57,1:50:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,she sometimes started to play with elementary schoolers 
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.84,1:50:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and she looked just as if she herself had been an elementary schooler
Dialogue: 0,1:50:30.82,1:50:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki-chan as the Education Chairperson
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.47,1:50:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,always tried to face each member sincerely, truthfully
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.66,1:50:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we consulted her for something,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:39.16,1:50:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,she tried to put herself in our shoes
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.48,1:50:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave deep consideration for us
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.52,1:50:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Among three of seniors, Saki-chan has been
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.93,1:50:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the girl of the most severe words
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.30,1:50:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And she was determined to create the best stage
Dialogue: 0,1:50:50.30,1:50:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,even though that made her disliked
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.74,1:50:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,or made her being scared
Dialogue: 0,1:50:55.80,1:50:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But we could always feel your love
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.94,1:51:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,when you gave us the harshest words
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.42,1:51:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Saki-chan
Dialogue: 0,1:51:05.52,1:51:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sara had believed myself to be bad at singing
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.20,1:51:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and honestly, I had disliked singing
Dialogue: 0,1:51:12.84,1:51:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But, without noticing it, I became to
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.15,1:51:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,hope to sing carefree, in my own way like Saki-chan
Dialogue: 0,1:51:19.39,1:51:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You made me love singing
Dialogue: 0,1:51:22.64,1:51:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I consulted you for singing skill
Dialogue: 0,1:51:24.60,1:51:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you encouraged me saying "You definitely can sing in a new way!"
Dialogue: 0,1:51:28.25,1:51:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sara surely will improve myself in singing
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.92,1:51:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please watch over me
Dialogue: 0,1:51:33.60,1:51:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:51:35.60,1:51:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And Isono Rinon-chan, the President of the student council
Dialogue: 0,1:51:38.49,1:51:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't read difficult kanji, much less write it
Dialogue: 0,1:51:41.77,1:51:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And she so often knows nothing about what an ordinary girl knows
Dialogue: 0,1:51:46.11,1:51:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She is very picky about vegetable
Dialogue: 0,1:51:48.41,1:51:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,When she was forced to drink the veggie smoothie
Dialogue: 0,1:51:50.41,1:51:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,as a penalty at the Transfer-ins Orientation event on June
Dialogue: 0,1:51:54.45,1:51:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the girl of no tears happened to cry
Dialogue: 0,1:51:59.36,1:52:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Such Rinon-chan whom we don't see how to make cry
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.91,1:52:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is really, truthfully a kind girl
Dialogue: 0,1:52:07.13,1:52:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She said "I'm trying to
Dialogue: 0,1:52:08.88,1:52:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,send something important directly in a way easy to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:52:12.70,1:52:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,for the young girls who have little vocabulary
Dialogue: 0,1:52:16.73,1:52:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She also said "I don't want to show my weakness"
Dialogue: 0,1:52:20.41,1:52:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"because I'm the senior now"
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.69,1:52:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She carried out her word and has been a cheerful Rinon-chan
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.47,1:52:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,without showing her frustration or sorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:52:32.04,1:52:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon-chan,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.21,1:52:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sara want to learn a lot more
Dialogue: 0,1:52:35.37,1:52:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,about Sakura Gakuin in these five years from you
Dialogue: 0,1:52:38.92,1:52:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,so that I can carry the good tradition to kouhais
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.41,1:52:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please keep being a good friend
Dialogue: 0,1:52:45.47,1:52:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and a wonderful senpai of us
Dialogue: 0,1:52:48.98,1:52:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,On the day before a concert,
Dialogue: 0,1:52:50.42,1:52:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon-chan and I made a sheet of setlist for the dressing room
Dialogue: 0,1:52:54.32,1:52:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and you told me the history of Sakura Gakuin
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.12,1:52:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or your mind while making the sheet
Dialogue: 0,1:52:59.93,1:53:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That moment was really precious
Dialogue: 0,1:53:03.32,1:53:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and fun for Sara
Dialogue: 0,1:53:05.08,1:53:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.03,1:53:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time I go to Sakura Gakuin,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.66,1:53:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when I enter the studio and give "Good Morning",
Dialogue: 0,1:53:14.26,1:53:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll not find three of you...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.82,1:53:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.45,1:53:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the fact. I don't want to think about it
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.85,1:53:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I feel very lonely
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.03,1:53:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for your graduation
Dialogue: 0,1:53:28.27,1:53:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But...What we must do now
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.16,1:53:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What we can do now is...
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.64,1:53:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep good tradition of Sakura Gakuin
Dialogue: 0,1:53:35.55,1:53:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,which senpais had created
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.28,1:53:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and to see you off with smiles,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:40.33,1:53:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,together with Fukei-sans, Mori-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,1:53:43.76,1:53:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Principal Kuramoto-sensei and staff teachers
Dialogue: 0,1:53:47.89,1:53:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Until now, we cried a lot
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.44,1:53:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,got scolded a lot, got angry a lot 
Dialogue: 0,1:53:52.98,1:53:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is my treasure
Dialogue: 0,1:53:55.23,1:53:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very very much
Dialogue: 0,1:53:58.29,1:54:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And, congratulation on your graduation
Dialogue: 0,1:54:01.71,1:54:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,on March 27, Heisei 28 year,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:04.99,1:54:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Current student representative
Dialogue: 0,1:54:06.67,1:54:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd grade in middle school, Kurashima Sara
